-Pekâlâ, onay verildi. Başlayın.
-Efendim.

363
00:28:09.200 --> 00:28:10.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
SAYIN BAŞKAN

364
00:28:51.240 --> 00:28:52.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İNANIYORUM Kİ

365
00:29:06.000 --> 00:29:09.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
